Subject to any regulations made under this Act, the management board may, in consultation with the Minister, determine the terms and conditions (including the payment of fees) on which—
(a) any health professional not in full-time service of the management board may be contracted by the management board — (i) to render ad hoc or part-time service to the management board ; or (ii) on part-time basis, to treat and attend upon patients of the hospital or health services;
